{"type": "article", "id": 9674, "title": "Goodwood NYC 木制时钟", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-18T07:23:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235639qgIPwDU61na3syMZ.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t纽约配饰品牌 Goodwood NYC 最近推出了一款木制时钟，这个叫做 “Retro J’s” 的时钟灵感来源为 Air Jordan 系列球鞋：时钟刻度即为 Air Jordan 1 到 Air Jordan 12 的鞋子设计，表盘采用的是桦木，色彩搭配简单舒适，极具质感。目前这款时钟有原色与灰色两款，售价 45 美元，<a href=\"http://www.goodwoodnyc.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235638Zg2wsIRlqyHUa05P.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235638o2sK0w3lPumcdUiM.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}